# c_idioms

# scanf skip rest of the line

~~~{.c .numberLines}
while (getchar() != '\n')
	;
~~~

# scanf skip blanks

~~~{.c .numberLines}
while ((ch = getchar()) == ' ')
	;
~~~

# length of an array
~~~{.c .numberLines}
int len = sizeof(a)/sizeof(a[0]);
~~~

#  linked list traversal idiom 
Visit nodes in a linked list, using a pointer variable `p` to keep track of the "current" node.

~~~{.c .numberLines}
for (p = first; p != NULL; p = p->next)
~~~


